doc.after: Basketball has been since 2000 one of the most popular sports in Pristina Pristina is represented in the Basketball National League by two teams  Streetball Kosova is a traditionally organised sport and cultural event at Germia Lake in Pristina since 2000 Football is also very popular Pristina s representatives KF Prishtina play their home games in the City Stadium
